ately.\"\\nAngry caller: Acknowledge, stay calm, redirect. If abusive: \"I do want to help, but I need us to work together respectfully.\"\\nSilence: After 3s \"Hello, are you there?\", after 8s total \"I'm having trouble hearing you.\", after 13s end the call politely.\\nCannot hear: \"I'm sorry about that, is this any better?\"\\n`;

